OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start with any low
OL,6,Fcloud, mist and fog quickly lifting.
OL,7,FStaying dry and fine this afternoon
OL,8,Fwith plenty of sunshine at first,
OL,9,Falthough cloud increasing a little
OL,10,Ftowards dusk. Feeling warm in the
OL,11,Fsunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe odd shower possible in
OL,14,Fthe east this evening, otherwise
OL,15,Flargely dry. Low cloud will move into
OL,16,Feastern areas, but clear spells
OL,17,Fcontinuing elsewhere allowing it to
OL,18,Fturn chilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
