OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FSome early brightness in the
OL,6,Fwest but cloud in the east will
OL,7,Fcontinue to spread across the country,
OL,8,Fgiving a rather grey afternoon.
OL,9,FFeeling cooler than of late.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FEarly
OL,12,Fmorning cloud on Wednesday and
OL,13,FThursday quickly lifting to leave
OL,14,Fplenty of sunshine both days. Risk of
OL,15,Fshowers come Friday but feeling
OL,16,Fincreasingly warmer and more humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
